From {{inh|ja|ojp|-|sort=つみは}}. First attested in the ''{{w|Nihon Shoki}}'' of 720 {{CE}}.<ref>{{R:Nihon Kokugo Daijiten 2|鍔・鐔}}</ref>

The final ''ha'' element is most likely cognate with {{m|ja|刃|tr=ha|t=edge}}.

Usually pronounced with {{rendaku|sort=つみば}}, as ''tsumiba''.

